message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper proposes a framework for estimation of fetal abdominal circumference from ultrasound images using a specially designed convolutional neural network (CNN). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which makes cs.MED (Medical Imaging) a possible sub-category. Finally, the use of neural networks in the proposed framework makes cs.NEURON (Neurons and Cognition) a possible sub-category as well.
